body:
I have changed the test case to use the EXTERNAL_SORT_MAX_MEMORY to configure the sort operator to use less memory instead of relying on MAX_QUERY_MEMORY_PER_NODE_KEY.

This way the test case passes all the time (it is failing intermittently in my branch).

@paul-rogers  can you please review this change.

kage
Also,  changed columnSizes in RecordBatchSizer from list to map so we can lookup using field names.

@Ben-Zvi can you please review ?

L" dataMode columns instead of "REQUIRED" ones

- Added supporting of specifying the DataMode of data type in MapWriter;
- Use nullable vectors in case of parent nested data type with OPTIONAL repetition.

1) Added <IF> <NOT> <EXISTS> support for CREATE TABLE
2) Added unit tests for the same

@paul-rogers please review
